& [LMStudioCorpusPrompt:integration_disposition_015_retry_001] is a non-mutating SOP worker retry prompt packet
  + [task_family] is integration_disposition
  + [retry_reason] is initial attempt had all fields and required terms but left outside empty and called validation pass despite a missing required literal term
  + [prompt_boundary] is prompt-only, no tools, no file reads, no repo mutation, no hidden-state claims
