      + [validation] is failed required literal term check
      + [integration_disposition] is retry after revision, not integrate
      + [evidence] is validation evidence shows fields present and one required literal absent
      + [outside] is autonomous integration, file changes, repo authority, hidden state access, and direct trust
      + [caution] is do not integrate until validation passes after revision
